✔️ Label Encoding

Convert all categorical columns into numeric using LabelEncoder.

✔️ Save Encoders

All label encoders saved using pickle for deployment consistency.

✔️ Imbalanced Dataset Handling

Used SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique) to balance:

Churn = Yes

Churn = No

SMOTE creates synthetic minority samples—improving recall and F1 score.
